{"tid":1789660,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［人手置頂］唔好以為用bitcoin就冇事","createTime":"2019-12-19T12:28:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T11:58:34.000Z","uid":86828,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"abac1524de8aadb5f44d7e1a578e9ce2db231cde","tid":1789660,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:28:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">TLDR：</span><br />\nbitcoin 唔係100% anonymous<br />\n如果搵到個address係屬於邊個都一樣會搵到你出黎 <br />\n要anonymous嘅話請用zcash, XMR 等真正保護私隱嘅幣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果係cryptocurrency呢個咁細嘅industry做過嘅話都會有聽過Chainalysis 呢間 track crpyto嘅公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chainalysis.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chainalysis.com%2F&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfMg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=b57ecf16\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chainalysis.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n而呢間野咁出名係因為連美國嘅稅局同DoJ都用緊呢套software<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而且有成功track到犯人嘅例子</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://blog.chainalysis.com/reports/chainalysis-doj-welcome-to-video-shutdown\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.chainalysis.com%2Freports%2Fchainalysis-doj-welcome-to-video-shutdown&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfMg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=4edc7a6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.chainalysis.com/reports/chainalysis-doj-welcome-to-video-shutdown</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cointelegraph.com/news/irs-uses-chainalysis-to-track-down-bitcoin-tax-cheats\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcointelegraph.com%2Fnews%2Firs-uses-chainalysis-to-track-down-bitcoin-tax-cheats&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfMg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=92bbe3a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://cointelegraph.com/news/irs-uses-chainalysis-to-track-down-bitcoin-tax-cheats</a><br />\n<br />\n而我有聽過同行講過d狗keep住都有去問呢個行業比較出名嘅公司有關<br />\n<br />\n1）cryptocurrency嘅原理係咩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">2）Chainalysis點用</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n所以提提大家<br />\n唔好以為會crpyto做donation就一定track唔到你<br />\nd狗識得用嘅話一樣會搵到你出黎 <br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好咁衝動去買bitcoin <br />\n上網做多d research先<br />\n如果唔係就<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想知多d嘅話可以係下面問<br />\n我盡量答（太technical未必識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"63836bc3af42e35941bb18590f885cd9e07ce058","tid":1789660,"uid":88940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:30:02.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">經濟攬炒！香港人果七千萬比人搞啊！佢老母仲OT成九億<br />\n1221<br />\n1224<br />\n1225<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n1221！星火已經唔得了 大家唔好喺今個星期六日和你shop<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789352\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789352</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n1224！［行動宜家唔推幾時推？］平安夜 賀佢老母呀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789301\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789301</a>"},{"pid":"840488162d44cfe01d110d7566fea3e5f0f0ae0b","tid":1789660,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:31:20.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56eb61aa61bb0f6d1078b56ffed75ee3d19f3e9","tid":1789660,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:31:47.000Z","msg":"好耐冇開過post